refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 arrayfalseposix_times




 Gets information about the current CPU usage.

  &reftitle.examples;



    Example use of posix_times


<?php

$times = posix_times();

print_r($times);
?>


    &example.outputs.similar;


Array
(
    [ticks] => 25814410
    [utime] => 1
    [stime] => 1
    [cutime] => 0
    [cstime] => 0
)

&reftitle.notes;



  This function isn't reliable to use, it may return negative values for
  high times.
